hopobject.name: show
hopobject.body: Too many people are looking for all of the presentation materials and not finding them. I'm working on moving all of them to http://beagleboard.org/show.
hopobject.shortdesc: This is a place to store links to the presentations given at various shows like Maker Faire, ESC/DesignEast/DesignWest and other shows BeagleBoard.org attends.
